{"tid":1103871,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"腳面貼唔到地 腳踝位會痛 應該睇咩醫生？","createTime":"2019-04-12T16:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T20:03:55.000Z","uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb125d18ddbcdf566e204ac7ab5b6930ce9cb278","tid":1103871,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20160329/photo/bkn-20160329121733891-0329_00982_001_07p.jpg?20160330122746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20160329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160329121733891-0329_00982_001_07p.jpg%3F20160330122746&h=bb7a1d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係做唔到佢咁 將小腿同腳面完全平放係地<br />\n左腳做到 但右腳唔得 直頭好似有野kick住咁<br />\n其實就咁旋轉腳踝 個跟腱都會痛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBhRkd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBhRkd9.png&h=712ce892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身以為只係由柔軟度唔夠 但死拉過幾次都無用<br />\n其實係咪有野移左位？應該照下x光定睇跌打？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610957017e095899dc66f0cfd23557397f5d8943","tid":1103871,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T20:00:52.000Z","msg":"有冇仆過撞過? 幾多年?"},{"pid":"fbdbe544c05187343e6c174926b23c78e2651e8d","tid":1103871,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T20:01:34.000Z","msg":"orz"},{"pid":"035ac8e1c9343c93786d06136673b665875ecbb9","tid":1103871,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T20:03:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}